title: Eyal Levi from Unstoppable Recording Machine & Daath
itunes:title: Eyal Levi from Unstoppable Recording Machine & Daath
description:
One afternoon I hopped on the phone with an old friend, Eyal Levi of the band Daath and producer at Unstoppable Recording Machine (unstoppablerecordingmachine.com) to discuss hustle & hard work, being under the microscope and burn out. This is a great episode for people looking to work in the music industry, but don't know where to start. Eyal is a hardworking guy that you can learn a thing or two from.
